   2896 Dec 17 13:07 gradlew.bat\n-rw-------   1 jovan jovan 892778000 Apr 21 09:10 java_pid1388798.hprof\n-rw-------   1 jovan jovan 891593888 Apr 21 09:14 java_pid1674774.hprof\n-rw-------   1 jovan jovan 891900342 Apr 21 08:23 java_pid372336.hprof\ndrwxrwxr-x 414 jovan jovan     20480 May  5 00:14 metadata\n-rw-rw-r--   1 jovan jovan       385 Apr  7 10:58 settings.gradle\ndrwxrwxr-x  11 jovan jovan      4096 May  3 12:46 skills\ndrwxrwxr-x 408 jovan jovan     20480 May  5 00:14 stats\ndrwxrwxr-x   3 jovan jovan      4096 Apr 30 09:29 test-results-native\ndrwxrwxr-x   6 jovan jovan      4096 Apr 30 23:50 tests\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
