est files; the scaffold placeholder was replaced with library-specific tests; reported dynamic-access coverage is 5/6, and the target CI checks are green. I found no blocking issues.\\\"'\",\"aggregated_output\":\"\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\n35:{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_19\",\"type\":\"agent_message\",\"text\":\"Submitted an approval review on PR `#5660`.\\n\\nI reviewed the authoritative `gh pr diff 5660 --name-only` and `--patch` output, confirmed the PR stays scoped to `software.amazon.awssdk:checksums:2.34.0`, checked that the scaffold placeholder was replaced with library-specific tests, verified reported dynamic-access coverage is `5/6` (>50%), and confirmed the relevant CI checks are green. I found no blocking issues.\"}}\n37:2026-05-04T07:14:53.116786Z ERROR codex_core::session: failed to record rollout items: thread 019df1d5-f142-77a1-8215-69a21bf2318a not found\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
